Slate's Culture Blog Jan. 24 2017 8:57 AM Here Is Your Complete List of 2017 Oscar Nominations, Including a Record-Tying 14 for La La Land La La Land ties the record for most ever nominations with 14, including Best Picture. Dale Robinette 
The nominations for the 89th Academy Awards were announced Tuesday morning, with La La Land leading the pack at 14, tying the all-time record with Titantic , Ben-Hur , and All About Eve for most-ever nominations.
